---

<PageLayout>
  <section class="flex items-center justify-center md:px-0">
    <AboutGallery client:visible/>
  </section>
  
  <!-- introduction to TBI -->
  <section class="md:flex items-center justify-center gap-20 px-6 md:px-2 lg:px-[15vh] pb-10 bg-nord6 ">
   
      
    <div class="md:w-[50%] mt-12">
      <div class="mb-6">
        <h1 class="text-4xl mb-4 md:block hidden">
          <SlidingText classes="text-nord10" text="Technology Business Incubator" stage={1} type="typewriter" client:visible/>
        </h1>
        <h1 class="md:hidden text-4xl mb-4 pt-8">
          <SlidingText classes="text-nord10" text="Technology Business" stage={0.75} type="slide up" client:visible/>
          <SlidingText classes="text-nord10" text="Incubator Society" stage={0.5} type="slide up" client:visible/>
        </h1>
      </div>

      <p class="text-nord2">
        Since 2012, BITS Pilani Hyderabad Campus Technology Business Incubator (TBI), 
        has been propelling technology-driven startups to new heights. With a mission 
        to encourage cutting-edge, knowledge-based entrepreneurship, TBIS provides a 
        launchpad for transformative ideas that aim to take off and make a lasting 
        impact in the real world. Originally established with support from the 
        National Science and Technology Entrepreneurship Development Board (NSTEDB), 
        Department of Science and Technology (DST), Government of India, TBIS continues 
        to thrive under the instituteâ€™s intramural funding, supporting entrepreneurs 
        on their journey from concept to lift-off.

      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12">
      <SecondaryAboutGallery pictures={pictures2} client:only="react"/>
    </div>
  </section>
  <hr class="h-1 border-0 bg-nord10" />
  <section class="py-8 bg-nord2">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 md:px-[25vh]">
      <h1 class="text-center text-4xl text-nord6 mb-5">
        Thrust Areas
      </h1>
      <div class="my-8 mt-8">
        <ThrustAreasCarousel client:visible/>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <hr class="h-1 border-0 bg-nord10" />

  <section class="md:flex items-center justify-center gap-24 px-6 md:px-2 lg:px-[35vh] pb-10 bg-nord6">
    <div id="team" class="my-6 scroll-mt-20">
      <div class="w-full py-8">
        <!-- Board Section -->
        <h1 class="text-4xl text-center text-nord10 mb-8 font-semibold">Governing and Operations</h1>
        <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <TeamCard
            name="Prof. V Ramgopal Rao"
            image="/governingandoperations/vrrao.jpg"
            description="Vice-Chancellor - Birla Institute of Technology & Science, Pilani and Chairman - TBIs"
          />
          <TeamCard
            name="Prof Soumyo Mukherji"
            image="/governingandoperations/Prof.SoumyoMukherji.png"
            description="Director - BITS Pilani, Hyderabad Campus and President, Technology Business Incubator"
          />
          <TeamCard
            name="Prof. P Yogeeswari"
            image="/governingandoperations/Prof.PYogeeswari.png"
            description="Chairperson - Technology Business Incubator, BITS Pilani, Hyderabad Campus"
          />
        </section>
      
        <!-- Team Section -->
        <h1 class="text-4xl text-center text-nord10 my-10 font-semibold">Team at TBI Office</h1>
        <section class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <TeamCard
            name="Mr. Sachin Arya"
            image="/governingandoperations/SachinArya.png"
            description="Chief Executive Officer, TBIs - Birla Institute of Technology & Science, Pilani"
          />
          <TeamCard
            name="Dr. Sandeep Raut"
            image="/governingandoperations/sandeepraut.jpg"
            description="General Manager - Technology and Business Incubator, BITS Pilani, Hyderabad Campus"
          />
          <TeamCard
            name="Mr. Mir Ali"
            image="/governingandoperations/mirali.jpeg"
            description="Assistant Manager - Technology and Business Incubator, BITS Pilani, Hyderabad Campus"
          />
        </section>
      </div>
      </section>
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  
</PageLayout>
